frames.caption: Two white peacocks stand gracefully at the entrance of a cave, overlooking a dramatic landscape. Lightning illuminates the stormy sky, casting a mystical glow on the scene. The peacocks' elegant feathers contrast with the dark, rugged cave surroundings.
frames.description: The scene captures two white peacocks at the mouth of a cave, set against a backdrop of a stormy landscape with lightning. The atmosphere is both serene and dramatic, with the natural beauty of the peacocks juxtaposed against the wildness of the storm.
